Neighbor3DColorVisualizer - Class in data.neighbors.hubness.visualization
This class helps with visualizing the kNN structure and the hubness of the data by visualizing it in 3D instead of 2D, which can help since any additional dimension makes for a better approximation of the skewness in the original high-dimensional space.
